imdb.plot outline: A four part web series that takes place over the course of a year. A documentary crew follow the strange and wonderful employees at the Office of Imaginary Assistance to the Lonely and are given an insight into the professional world of imaginary friends. We meet the typical workers; the jock, the burn out, the newbies, the should-be couple and the overly confident boss as they try to help their lonely clients get their lives back on track.
imdb.title: UnImaginary
plot: A Documentary crew follow the lives of the strange and wonderful employees at the Office of Imaginary Assistance to the Lonely, as they try their best to be the semi-imaginary friends they think their clients need.
